edu.monash.fit2099.interfaces

Interface ActionInterface

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Action, AimAction, AttackAction, ChooseWeaponAction, CraftAction, DoNothingAction, DropItemAction, EatAction, GoToMainMenuAction, HarvestAction, KickAction, MoveActorAction, PickUpItemAction, QuitAction, ReloadAction, SelectTargetAction, ShootAction, ShootTargetAction, SowCropAction, SpitBehaviour, WindowSmashAction

    public interface ActionInterface
    This interface provides the ability to add methods to Action, without modifying code in the engine, or down casting references in the game.
